cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SE

This paper deals with security-related applications of machine learning, specifically the poisoning attack against SVM. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves machine learning algorithms and techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper proposes a method to protect the SVM classifier, which could also place it in the cs.SE (Software Engineering) category.
